Lunch Unremitting misery for Australia. England lead by 356 after hurtling along that session. So, it seems that Paul Collingwood is retiring from Test cricket having helped the team retain the Ashes in Australia, and with a series win also on the cards. For most Australians, the enduring memory of Collingwood's Test career will be his 206 at Adelaide Oval four years ago.
